Release Updates

Commerce enhancements include new features for 
B2B and D2C Commerce, Salesforce Order Management, and Salesforce Payments.

Salesforce B2C and D2C Commerce
Updated Commerce app with customizable store templates and Salesforce Checkout for seamless payment and tax setup.
Automate tax calculations and reporting on global payments with Salesforce Tax Solution.
Enable automatic index rebuilds and use Data Cloud for actionable insights into ecommerce business.

Salesforce Order Management
Easily replace shopper items using enhanced exchanges in UI via flows. Manage orders in bulk with large order support for cancellations, returns.

Salesforce Payments
Configure PayPal and add merchant account to D2C store using Salesforce Checkout. Streamline customer purchases with one-click checkout. Get Pay Now with new license independent of Commerce license.
